<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2287">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3599">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ جَعْفَرٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رَأَيْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَأْكُلُ الرُّطَبَ بِالْقِثَّاءِ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>